name: Jack Irish
overview: Jack Irish is a man getting his life back together again. A former criminal lawyer whose world imploded, he now spends his days as a part-time investigator, debt collector, apprentice cabinet maker, punter and sometime lover – the complete man really. An expert in finding those who don’t want to be found – dead or alive, Jack helps out his mates while avoiding the past. That is until the past finds him.

seasons.name: Series 1
seasons.overview: Jack is tasked with finding a missing person only to find himself framed for his murder and caught up in a conspiracy. With twists and turns at every step and run-ins with dynamic characters along the way, Jack’s investigations takes audiences on a whirlwind adventure from the streets of Fitzroy in Melbourne to a remote village the Philippines.

seasons.name: Series 2
seasons.overview: A foreign student studying in Australia passes away after she is fatally hit by a bus in Melbourne’s CBD. Irish, together with his partner in crime Cam Delray, must investigate the suspicious circumstances surrounding her death, including the potential for a stalker who may have been following her.

seasons.name: Series 3
seasons.overview: Emmy award-winner Guy Pearce is back for one last crusade reprising his iconic role as Jack Irish, a former criminal lawyer with a penchant for getting wrapped up in things he shouldn’t.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Jack Irish finds himself staring down the barrel of a brand new case, but something goes awry and Jack ends up framed for murder. While it seems it is curtains for Jack, an alibi turns up out of the blue.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Jack enlists Linda in the hunt for a lead in Manila. Meanwhile, Jack & Sarah grow closer as they search for Tina. As the trail gets warmer, Jack is ambushed & warned that he could be the next victim in this murderous game.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Jack is determined to uncover who framed him for murder. Linda gets a lead to an interview and despite warnings, puts herself in danger.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: A tense night in the Filipino jungle results in a chance discovery for Linda and Orton. Jack's concerned for Sarah's well-being as she becomes consumed by manic determination following news about Tina.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Jack struggles to recuperate and his mind takes an increasingly turn towards Rob Shand. Back in Manila, Linda is abducted. Longmore refuses to act against the church leaving Jack alone to fight for Sarah.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Jack is now on the run from both the police and members of Via Crucis. Terrified yet resolved, Linda finally comes face to face with her captor.

episodes.name: The Last Post
episodes.overview: After Eddie, a Chinese courier who was supposed to deliver a package for Jack three years ago, shows up dead, Jack can't help but get involved. Following the trail of Eddie's last movements, Jack discovers Eddie's friend, an Indian student named Lakshmi, committed suicide shortly before Eddie disappeared. They studied together at a private college where the facilities and level of education leave much to be desired

episodes.name: Deal With The Dead
episodes.overview: As Jack Irish investigates two deaths, he delves deeper into the murky world of international colleges.

episodes.name: From The Ashes
episodes.overview: As Jack Irish discovers more about the two deaths, he isn’t sure who he can trust.

episodes.name: The A-List
episodes.overview: Secrets are revealed as Jack Irish’s investigation stretches to the colourful streets of Mumbai.

episodes.name: Sins Of Omission
episodes.overview: As Jack Irish gets closer to the truth, his investigation threatens to tear his world apart.

episodes.name: Returning Home
episodes.overview: In the season final, Jack Irish fights to unmask the truth, but will this fight for justice be his last?

episodes.name: Hell Bent (Part 1)
episodes.overview: After the execution-style death of an off-duty cop, Barry Tregear calls in a favour with Jack, leading him on the path to uncovering a buried truth about his murdered wife, Isabel.

episodes.name: Hell Bent (Part 2)
episodes.overview: As the body count rises, Jack seeks help from Linda, the pair of them working together to dig deeper into what Barry knew about Isabel's death

episodes.name: Hell Bent (Part 3)
episodes.overview: The countdown to payday begins as Jack hunts down Barry's killer but as the truth begins to come out, Jack's world is turned upside down.
